QuestionTxt: Do you think Russia's attempts to influence the (2016) presidential election using cyberattacks helped Donald Trump or helped Hillary Clinton, or do you think they had no real effect? Do you think Russia helped Clinton/Trump a lot or just a little?
StudyNote: 426 respondents were interviewed on a landline telephone, and 591 were interviewed on a cell phone. Interviews were conducted by Braun Research.
